<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111528>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Merodon antenna, lateral view. A Merodon eumerusi sp. n. male, inner side, B Merodon eumerusi sp. n. male, outer side, C Merodon eumerusi sp. n. female, inner side, D Merodon eumerusi sp. n. female, outer side, E Merodon pumilus Macquart male, outer side, F Eumerus armatus Ricarte et Rotheray male, outer side, G Eumerus truncatus Rondani male, outer side. f—fossette. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111528/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111530>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Head of Merodon eumerusi sp. n.. A, C lateral view, B, D dorsal view. A, B male, C, D female. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111530/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111532>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Male of Merodon eumerusi sp. n.. lateral view. Scale bar, 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111532/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111534>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Metafemur of Merodon male. A, B Merodon eumerusi sp. n., C Merodon segetum (Fabricius), D Eumerus truncatus. A, anterior view, B, C, D antero-ventral view. it—row of inner thorns. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111534/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111536>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Abdomen of Merodon eumerusi sp. n., dorsal view. A male, B female. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111536/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111538>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Male genitalia of Merodon, epandrium. A, B Merodon eumerusi sp. n., C, D Merodon ottomanus. A, C lateral view, B, D ventral view. al—anterior surstyle lobe, pl—posterior surstyle lobe, c—cercus. Scale bar, 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111538/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111540>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Male genitalia of Merodon, hypandrium, lateral view. A Merodon eumerusi sp. n., B Merodon ottomanus. vr— ventral ridge, s—lateral sclerite of aedeagus. Scale bar, 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111540/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

